value:
This castle is so beautiful, I feel like
I've become a princess! I wish I
could just stay here forever...

Me? Well... I was raised at a priory.
I do have a father... But I can't see
him. I really wish I could.

I'm a little worried about you! You're
always running around. You should
follow my lead and take a nap.

I'm writing a story. Actually... I want
someone to read it. Do you think you
might have time later? Only if it's OK.

...
...
...$k$pOh! Sorry, sorry! I was thinking
about this new idea I had for a story.
Would you like to hear about it?

Excuse me... I was asked to
bring you this greeting from
$Nf.
Yay! I'm getting stronger, aren't I?
Oh, this makes me so happy!

How exciting! Do I seem any
different to you?

My name is Genny. Since I barely
know anybody here...I'm a little
anxious. I hope we can get along.

Can I ask you something? I'd like it
if you would visit more often. Will you
spend some time with me?$k$pIf you find the time, we could drink
tea or go for a walk in the woods or
around the lake...$k$pIs that too much to ask? I know you
already come and see me a lot.
I don't want you to get tired of me.$k$pPeople always tell me that I'm like
a little sister, but I want you to see
me as more than that.$k$pI'll do my best to get stronger and
stand on my own two feet. I really
hope you'll see what I mean.
You know... If I could, I'd like to meet my father.
Just so you know...I'd do whatever I could to help.
